    <section id="mission">
        <h3>Our Vision & Mission</h3>
        <p>
            We envision a world where every person has the opportunity to live a life of dignity and purpose. We believe
            that the best way to achieve this is by creating jobs that empower people to break the cycle of poverty.
        </p>


    </section>


